Studies show that being surrounded by #nature helps us feel calmer, purifies toxins from the air, and makes us happier. 🌱

If you #love #plants as much as we do, then you would love @rootednyc. #Rooted partners with local growers so that plants are shipped directly from nurseries to you. They spend less time in transit and arrive healthier and happier. 🌿
⠀
Plus, they're part of the @1percentftp, which means a percentage of all their sales — profit or not — goes directly to supporting environmental charities around the #world. 🌵
⠀
Ready to create your very own indoor #jungle? Head to rooted.nyc/pride and use the code pride to receive 15% off your first order. 🌱
